      "imageUrl": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/stray-bullets/images/7/7e/StrayBullets_02.jpg",
      "description": "Stray Bullets is an independent American comic book series published in black and white (with color covers) by El Capitan Books and Image Comics. It is written and drawn by David Lapham.\n\nThe story deals with the often criminal and sometimes tragic misadventures of a large cast of characters and takes place from the mid-1970s through the mid-1990s. Published on an irregular basis since 1995, the comic has had close to 100 issues and is a long-time critically acclaimed series.",
